history.content:
Please make sure that in Gradescope your SID matches your student id on TSquare (this is something like evigoda77, not the 9-digit number).  Also check that your full name is there and correct.  Otherwise we can't match your Gradescope page with your Proctortrack+TSquare entries, so we won't be able to give you a grade.  

For example, some names and SID's are missing or rubbish.  And one student has a non-GT email address for their login.  Please correct if you'd like a grade.

--Eric
